{
  "text": "At reperfusion 24 hr after MCAO injury, rat were sacrificed and brains were washed rapidly with ice-cold PBS, and collected. Tissues were lysed with ice-cold RIPA buffer (Sigma-Aldrich, St. Louis, MO, USA). The lysates were centrifuged at 13,200 rpm for 1 hr at 4\u00b0C to produce whole-cell extracts. Protein content was quantified using the BCA method (Pierce, Rockford, IL, USA). Protein (20 \u03bcg [CITATION_1] .",
